Products.RichDescription:
Woolworths Brown Rice Cups are steamed, nutritious whole grain rice that's ready in seconds.

Why not try... Mediterranean brown rice. For a meal that's ready in minutes, toss rice together with a tin of tuna, cherry tomatoes, sliced cucumber, tinned sweet corn kernels and parsley.

Source of fibre.

Microwave 40 secs.

Naturally gluten free.

No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.
